### DrCal API - Testes de Serviços Profissionais
### Este arquivo contém exemplos de requisições para testar as rotas de serviços profissionais

### 1. Criar um novo serviço profissional
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Consulta",
  "duration_minutes": 30
}

### 2. Criar outro serviço profissional
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Retorno",
  "duration_minutes": 15
}

### 3. Criar serviço com duração maior
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Procedimento Especializado",
  "duration_minutes": 60
}

### 4. Listar todos os serviços de um profissional
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 5. Buscar serviço por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 6. Atualizar serviço
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Consulta Especializada",
  "duration_minutes": 45
}

### 7. Atualizar apenas o nome do serviço
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Consulta de Rotina"
}

### 8. Atualizar apenas a duração
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "duration_minutes": 40
}

### 9. Excluir serviço (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 10. Teste de validação - Campos obrigatórios faltando
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Teste"
}

### 11. Teste de validação - Duração inválida
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Teste",
  "duration_minutes": 0
}

### 12. Teste de validação - Duração negativa
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Teste",
  "duration_minutes": -10
}

### 13. Teste de validação - ID inválido
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/invalid-uuid
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 14. Teste de validação - Profissional inexistente
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/services
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 15. Teste de validação - Serviço inexistente
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 16. Teste sem autenticação
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services

### 17. Teste com API key inválida
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services
x-api-key: invalid-api-key

### 18. Teste de atualização com duração inválida
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/{{SERVICE_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "duration_minutes": -5
}

### 19. Teste de exclusão de serviço inexistente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 20. Teste de atualização de serviço inexistente
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "service_name": "Serviço Inexistente"
}

### Variáveis para testes:
# API_KEY: Sua API key válida
# PROFESSIONAL_ID: ID de um profissional criado
# SERVICE_ID: ID de um serviço criado 